1) proc double dmg (starts at lvl 51 i think) I forget the exact reqs for this, but mob has to be standing still and there cnat be a bunch of mobs/pcs around it (like i said not totally sure how this works)<br>
<br>
2) archery mastery, this aa ability gives up to 100% increase on bow dps (class aa for rangers with 3 steps)<br>
<br>
