<br>
Now these are what makes rangers do decent dps with bows, and warriors would get none of this nor am I saying we should get these 3 things. All I am saying is give us endless quiver, which gives you unlimited arrows of a ammo slot and the innate  quiver effect, hell take off the quiver effect for warriros, I filling 10-20 slots on stupid fletching supplies or bugging the crap out of a mage. <br>
