Range fighters, such as casters are pretty annoyed by the fact that its impossible to sit and med within casting range if they get a snare or root in.<br>
A good 150+ range bow and 150 range arrows hits a range fighter whereever they are.<br>
Most caster spells has a standard range of 200 and with focus they hit a max range of 250, so 300 will push them far away.<br>
Its important that the skill is high, because with a low skill you can easily miss even a sitting target and then they are not interrupted in their meditation. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><p align="center">
